---
source: crates/runtime/tests/search/mod.rs
description: "SELECT id, trunc(_score, 3) as _score  FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by _score desc, id desc LIMIT 4;"
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: _score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                   |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer)._score, Int64(3)) AS _score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[_score, id]                                                        |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@1 DESC, id@0 DESC], fetch=4                                                                            |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@1 DESC, id@0 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@0 AS Int64) as id, trunc(1 - distance@1, 3) as _score]                                               |
|               |       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                   |
|               |         RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                            |
|               |           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                            |
|               |             CooperativeExec                                                                                                             |
|               |               S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): limit=100                                                                              |
|               |                                                                                                                                         |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
